1a:T4ba,Internal evidence clearly identifies this as the Auric LPS (Locking Plate System) Clavicle Plates family. Brand is 'Auric', manufacturer is Meril Life Sciences. Product is a specific anatomical plate system for clavicle fractures with distinctive TiNb gold coating (Bionik Gold Surface). The description specifies superior anterior plates with optional lateral extension, pre-contoured S-shape design, and dual hole diameters (2.7mm/3.5mm) indicating variable angle locking capability. Entity type is product_family as this represents a complete line of clavicle plates with different configurations (with/without lateral extension). However, review is required because: (1) No external verification available, (2) Brand field was empty in source data requiring inference from product_family and brochure_heading, (3) Need to confirm if 'LPS' is proprietary naming or generic descriptor for locking plate system. Classification is internally consistent but lacks external validation. Material specification shows titanium with TiNb coating at 3.0mm thickness, which is clinically appropriate for clavicle plating. Confidence set to 0.85 due to strong internal consistency but absence of external corroboration.16:["$","$L19",null,{"product":{"product_name":"Auric LPS Clavicle Plates","product_name_display":"LPS Clavicle Plates","sku_code":"MRL-TRA-004","product_family":"Auric LPS Clavicle Plates","product_family_display":"Auric LPS Clavicle Plates","slug":"auric-lps-clavicle-plates","images":[{"id":"prop_69c49a1","storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/69c17bd504841ec9248cfac3/cover_ec4e4072.jpg","original_filename":"cover_Auric Brochure.pdf.jpg","content_type":"image/jpeg","size":325576,"uploaded_at":"2026-03-26T05:54:29.477848+00:00","source":"family_propagation","width":1654,"height":2339}],"status":"published","live_visible":true,"brochure_url":"","seo_meta_title":"LPS Clavicle Plates | Auric Locking Plates - MedDevice Pro Telangana","seo_meta_description":"Superior anterior c